tourBios.personal: Earliest golf memory is playing with his father and grandfather in Kauai...Biggest thrills in golf include winning the Pac-12 title, winning the NCAA Regional Championship and firing a 66 in the second round of the PGA TOUR's U.S. Bank Championship in Milwaukee...Would like to trade places with a Navy SEAL for a day...Favorite pro teams are the Chicago White Sox, Chicago Bulls and Chicago Bears...Dream foursome includes his father, Michael Jordan and Tiger Woods...Once met Jordan during a round of golf...Golf courses he would like to play are Pine Valley in New Jersey and Augusta National in Georgia...Twitter handle is @jesler66.
